\s1 The Exodus, Wandering, and Conquest Reviewed  
\p
\v 2  Moses proclaimed \w to|strong="H7200"\w* \w all|strong="H7200"\w* Israel \w as|strong="H1992"\w* follows: “\w You|strong="H7200"\w* \w have|strong="H5869"\w* \w seen|strong="H7200"\w* \w all|strong="H7200"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \nd Lord\nd* \w did|strong="H5869"\w* \w in|strong="H1419"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* land \w of|strong="H5869"\w* Egypt \w to|strong="H7200"\w* Pharaoh, \w all|strong="H7200"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* servants, \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* land.  
