\v 6  \w You|strong="H5221"\w* \w have|strong="H4428"\w* eaten no bread \w and|strong="H4428"\w* drunk no wine \w or|strong="H4428"\w* beer – \w all|strong="H3318"\w* \w so|strong="H3318"\w* \w that|strong="H4428"\w* \w you|strong="H5221"\w* \w might|strong="H4725"\w* know \w that|strong="H4428"\w* \w I|strong="H2088"\w* am \w the|strong="H5221"\w* \nd Lord\nd* \w your|strong="H3318"\w* God!  
