\v 18  Beware \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* \w heart|strong="H3820"\w* \w of|strong="H1697"\w* \w no|strong="H1961"\w* \w man|strong="H6771"\w*, woman, clan, \w or|strong="H8085"\w* tribe among \w you|strong="H3588"\w* turns \w away|strong="H3212"\w* \w from|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* \nd Lord\nd* \w our|strong="H1288"\w* God today \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w pursue|strong="H3212"\w* \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w serve|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* gods \w of|strong="H1697"\w* \w those|strong="H8085"\w* nations; beware \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w is|strong="H3820"\w* among \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w no|strong="H1961"\w* root producing poisonous \w and|strong="H3212"\w* bitter fruit.  
\v 19  \w When|strong="H3588"\w* \w such|strong="H2088"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w person|strong="H5545"\w* hears \w the|strong="H3605"\w* words \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w this|strong="H2088"\w* oath \w he|strong="H1931"\w* secretly blesses \w himself|strong="H1931"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* says, “\w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* peace \w though|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* continue \w to|strong="H3068"\w* walk \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* stubborn spirit.” \w This|strong="H2088"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w destroy|strong="H4229"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* watered ground \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* parched.  
